        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Deuteronomy 11</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Deut-011-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואהבת</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            Da süvgün Adonaj Tenrijni da saqlaɣyn saqlavyn anyn da resim-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            lerin da törelerin anyn da micvalaryn bar ol künlerde.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Deut-011-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וידעתם </foreign>
                            Da bilijiz bügün ki tüvül ulanlaryjyz byla ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            bilmediler da ki körmediler ošol tyjuvun Adonajnyn Tenrijiz-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            nin ošol u<supplied reason="lost">l</supplied>luluɣun anyn ošol qudratyn
                            ol küčlü da quvatyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            anyn ol sunulɣan.</l><l n="3" xml:id="Deut-011-003"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da ošol belgilerin anyn da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            ošol išlerin ki qyldy ortasynda Micrinin parʿoɣa biji-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ne Micrinin da bar jerine anyn.</l><l n="4" xml:id="Deut-011-004"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואשר </foreign>
                            Da neki qyldy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            čerüvüne Micrinin a<supplied reason="lost">tl</supplied>aryna<ref
                                target="#fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> anyn da markavyna ki jüzdür-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            dü ošol suvlaryn Jam Sufnun jüzleri üstüne alarnyn quv-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            ɣanlarynda siznin artyna da tasetti alarny Adonaj ošpu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            küngedejin.</l><l n="5" xml:id="Deut-011-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואשר </foreign>
                            Da neki qyldy sizge midbarda
                            <milestone unit="page" n="299v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            kelgenijizgedejin ošpu orunɣadejin.</l><l n="6" xml:id="Deut-011-006"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואשר </foreign>
                            Da neki qyldy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Datanɣa da Aviramɣa ulanlaryna Eliʾavnyn uvlunun Ruʾuven-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            nin ki ačty ol jer ošol avzun da juttu alarny da ošol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            üvlerin alarnyn da ošol čatyrlaryn alarnyn da ošol bar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            ol ḥalqny ki alar qatyna ortasynda bar Jisraʾelnin.</l><l n="7"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            Ki közlerijizdi ol körüvčüler ošol bar išlerin Adonajnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            ol ullu ki qyldy.</l><l n="8" xml:id="Deut-011-008"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושמרתם </foreign>
                            Da saqlajyz ošol bar ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            micvany ki men bujuramen saja bügün anyn üčün ki küčejgejsiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            da kelgejsiz da mereslegejsiz ošol ol jerni ki siz ašasiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            ary meresleme any.</l><l n="9" xml:id="Deut-011-009"><addSpan
                                spanTo="#add001" />ן<supplied reason="lost"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                    style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולמע</foreign>
                            </supplied><anchor xml:id="add001" /> Da anyn üčün ki uzartqajsiz kün-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            ler ol jer üstüne ki antetti Adonaj atalaryjyzɣa ber-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            me alarɣa da urluɣuna alarnyn jer aɣadoɣan süt da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            bal.</l><l n="10" xml:id="Deut-011-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי </foreign>
                            Ki ol jer ki sen kelesen ary meresleme
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            any tüvüldü jeri kibik Micrinin ol ki čyqtyjyz andan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            ki čačsajedij ošol urluɣujnu da kerekli edi ki suɣar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            ɣajsen ajaɣyjbyla baɣyn kibik ol ješilliknin.</l><l n="11"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והארץ </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ol jer ki siz ašasiz ary meresleme any jer tavly da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            enišli jamɣurundan ol köklernin ičedi suv.</l><l n="12"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ארץ</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            Jer ki Adonaj Tenrij tergejdi any hammeše ʿenajatlary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            Adonaj Tenrijnin anda bašlyɣyndan ol jylnyn da sofunadejin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            jylnyn.</l><l n="13" xml:id="Deut-011-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והיה </foreign>
                            Da bolɣaj eger tynlama tynlasajyz micva-
                            <milestone unit="page" n="300r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            laryma ki men bujuramen sizge bügün süvme <addSpan spanTo="#add002"
                                 />qulluɣun<anchor xml:id="add002" /> Adonajnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Tenrijiznin da qulluq etme anar bar jüregijizbyla da bar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ǯanyjyzbyla.</l><l n="14" xml:id="Deut-011-014"><addSpan
                                spanTo="#add003" /><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ונתתי</foreign>
                            <anchor xml:id="add003" /> Da berirmen jamɣurun jerijiznin vaḥtynda
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            jazɣy jamɣurnun da küzdegi jamɣurnun da jyštyryrsen
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            bürtügüjnü da šarbetijni da sajyjny.</l><l n="15" xml:id="Deut-011-015"
                                ><supplied reason="lost"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                    style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ונתתי</foreign>
                            </supplied> Da ašarsen da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            tojarsen da berirmen kögöt tüzüjde tuvaryja da.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Deut-011-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">השמרו </foreign>
                            Saqlanyjyz özüjüzge maɣat jeldenir jüregijiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            da qajyrylyrsiz jaḥšy joldan da qulluq etersiz özge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            tenrilerge da bašurursiz alarɣa.</l><l n="17" xml:id="Deut-011-017"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וחרה </foreign>
                            Da qabunur
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            ačuvu Adonajnyn sizge da bekler ošol ol köklerni da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            bolmasty jamɣur da ol jer bermesti ošol bitišin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            da taspolur<supplied reason="lost">siz</supplied><ref target="#fn2"
                                type="noteAnchor" /> tez ol jaḥšy jer üstün<supplied reason="lost"
                                >den</supplied><ref target="#fn3" type="noteAnchor" /> ki Adonaj Ten-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            rijiz beredi sizge.</l><l n="18" xml:id="Deut-011-018"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושמתם </foreign>
                            Da qojujuz ošol söz-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            lerimni ošpularny jüregijizge da ǯanyjyzɣa da bajlajyz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            alarny belgige qolujuz üstüne da bolsunlar totafot-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            qa közlerijiz arasyna.</l><l n="19" xml:id="Deut-011-019"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולמדתם </foreign>
                            Da üvretijiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            alarny uvullaryjyzɣa sözleme alarny olturɣanyjda üvüj-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            de da jürügenijde jolda da jatqanyjdan burun da turɣa-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            nyjdan sortun.</l><l n="20" xml:id="Deut-011-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וכתבתם </foreign>
                            Da <addSpan spanTo="#add004" />qyjasa<anchor xml:id="add004" /> jazɣyn
                            alarny odv́erjalary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            üstüne üvlerijnin da qabaqlaryjda <seg type="commented" n="#seg001" />ki
                            hammeše bol-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ɣaj sözleri Toranyn esijde<anchor type="commented" xml:id="seg001"
                                 /><ref target="#fn4" type="noteAnchor" />.</l><l n="21"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">למען </foreign>
                            Anyn üčün
                            <milestone unit="page" n="300v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            ki artqajlar künlerijiz da künleri ulanlaryjyznyn ol jer
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            üstüne ki antetti Adonaj atalaryjyzɣa berme alar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ɣa künlerikibik ol köklernin ol jerbyla.</l><l n="22"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            Ki eger saqlama saqlasajyz ošol bar ol micvany ošpu-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            nu ki men bujuramen sizge qylma any süvme ošol qul-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            luɣun Adonaj Tenrijnin jürüme bar jollarybyla anyn da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            jabušma qulluɣuna anyn.</l><l n="23" xml:id="Deut-011-023"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והוריש </foreign>
                            Da taseter
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Adonaj ošol bar ol ḥanlyqlarny ošpularny alnyjyzdan da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            mereslersiz ḥanlyqlarny ulluraqlarny da küčlüreklerni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            sizden.</l><l n="24" xml:id="Deut-011-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כל </foreign>
                            Bar ol orun ki bassa ta<supplied reason="lost">ba</supplied>ny<ref
                                target="#fn5" type="noteAnchor" /> ajaɣyjyznyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            anda sizge bolur bašlap ol midbardan da ol Levanondan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ol ullu özenden özeninden Peratnyn da ol maʿarav-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            sarɣy tengizgedejin bolur čegijiz.</l><l n="25" xml:id="Deut-011-025"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">לא </foreign>
                            Turalmasty ki-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            šide alnyjyzda qorquvujuznu da qobuvujuznu berir
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            Adonaj Tenrijiz jüzleri üstüne bar ol jernin ki bassajyz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            anda ki nečik sözledi sizge.
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פרשת ראה
                                אנכי</foreign>
                        </l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                        <l n="26" xml:id="Deut-011-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ראה אנכי נתן לפניכם היום </foreign>
                            Baqqyn men beremen
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            alnyjzda bügün alɣyšny da qarɣyšny.</l><l n="27" xml:id="Deut-011-027"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">את</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="page" n="301r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            Ošol ol alɣyšny ki tynlasajyz micvalaryna Adonaj Tenrijiz-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            nin ki men bujuramen sizge bügün.</l><l n="28" xml:id="Deut-011-028"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והקללה </foreign>
                            Da ol qarɣyš-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ny eger tynlamasajyz micvalaryna Adonaj Tenrijiznin da ketsejiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            ol joldan ki men bujuramen sizge bügün barma qulluɣu ar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            tyna özge tenrilernin ki bilmejsiz.</l><l n="29" xml:id="Deut-011-029"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והיה </foreign>
                            Da bolɣaj
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            ki keltirse seni Adonaj Tenrij ol jerge ki sen kelesen ary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            meresleme any da bergin ošol ol alɣyšny tavy üs-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            tüne Gerizimnin da ošol ol qarɣyšny tavy üstü-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            ne ʿEvalnyn.</l><l n="30" xml:id="Deut-011-030"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הלא </foreign>
                            Muna alar köčüvünde ol Jarden-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            nin maʿaravsary jolusary enüvünün ol qujašnyn jerinde
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            ol Kenaʿaninin ol olturuvču jylɣalyqta uturusuna ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            G<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>lgalnyn<ref target="#fn6"
                                type="noteAnchor" /> janynda tüz jerlerinin Morenin.</l><l n="31"
                            xml:id="Deut-011-031"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי </foreign>
                            Ki siz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            ašasiz ošol ol Jardenni kelme meresleme ošol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ol jerni ki Adonaj Tenrijiz beredi sizge da mereslesejiz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            any da oltursajyz anda.</l><l n="32" xml:id="Deut-011-032"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושמרתם </foreign>
                            Da saqlajyz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            qylma ošol bar ol resimlerni da ošol ol töreler-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ni ki men beremen alnyjyzda bügün.</l></ab>
                </div>
